    "attributes": {
        "action": "Stop all Universal Credit Reviews and Bank Statement requests",
        "additional_details": "",
        "background": "We believe it is an invasion of privacy to have to provide several months of bank statements and other documents to obtain Universal Credit. We think that if a benefit claimant is breaking the law, this should be charged as an offence and proven in court.",
